    "description_long": "This is a compact, handheld radio receiver with a prominent telescopic antenna extending from the top. The front face features a digital display screen, several tactile buttons arranged in a grid, and a visible brand label above the screen. The body is primarily black with a matte finish, and there is a small decorative sticker near the bottom. The sides include a push-to-talk button and a belt clip, while the back is solid with visible screws and a battery compartment. The overall design is rugged, suitable for outdoor or urban use, and the device appears to be constructed mainly from durable plastic with some metal components.",
